data.description: Come live among the trees! Recently renovated home located in a forest like setting is turn-ley ready for move in. An open concept floor plan greets you as you enter. Updated flooring & a neutral color scheme throughout the property will make decorating a breeze. Vaulted ceilings & sky lights provide vast amounts of light. Fresh cabinetry in the kitchen provides massive amounts of storage & stone countertops offer ample space for all your small appliances. The master suite in equipped with a spa like bathroom retreat & the additional three bedrooms have fresh carpeting. A second bath also gives easy access to the additional living spaces. An expansive driveway provides ample parking & the backyard is large enough to give the kids plenty of space. Side gate is also big enough to fit cars/trailers to store in backyard. Easy access to I-45 North & FM 1960. Book your viewing today. . Call the listing agent for more questions to schedule a privet showing. Room dimensions are approximate.
